ui <- 
  material_depth(
    depth = 2,
    material_row(
      id = "treecontrols",
      title = "",
      class = "center",
      material_column(
        width = 4,
        offset = 2,
        switchInput(
          inputId = "edible-switch",
          "",
          value = F,
          inline = T,
          size = 'mini', 
          onStatus = "success"
        ),
        disabled(
          radioButtons(
            "edible",
            label = "Edible Trees",
            choices = c("Fruit", "Nut"),
            inline = T
          )
        )
      ),
      material_column(
        width = 4,
        switchInput(
          "value-switch",
          "",
          value = T,
          inline = T,
          size = 'mini',
          onStatus = "success"
        ),
        radioButtons(
          "value",
          label = "Tree Value",
          choices = c("Total", "Per Acre"),
          inline = T
        ),
                bsTooltip(id = "edible", title = "Edible trees", 
                  trigger = "hover",
                  placement = "left"),
      )
    )
  )

server <- function(input, output, session) {
  addTooltip(session, id = "edible", title = "This is an input.",
           placement = "left", trigger = "hover")
}
